        "setup": "Generate or retrieve the API key from your CRM or lead-provider integration that you configure in realtor.com Lead Settings. In the realtor.com dashboard, go to **Settings → Lead Settings → Connections Plus → Add a Lead Delivery API** and enter the key from the third-party CRM/application you are connecting. Realtor.com’s docs say the key is provided by the CRM provider, not minted inside realtor.com. See [Lead API Integration](https://support.realtor.com/s/lead-api-integration) and [Lead API Quick Start](https://support.realtor.com/s/lead-api-quick-start)."
